        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1671847778" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6416882612823988903">Hahahaha! This book is so out of date, Goodreads doesn&apos;t even have a cover image. It&apos;s early Tuchman, her break-out book, I believe. As with her other wonderful histories, I learn so much I almost can&apos;t believe it. So that&apos;s how we got into World War I. So we did save their butts. What would have happened if we didn&apos;t? Amazing on so many levels.</span>
  <span id="freeText6416882612823988903" style="display:none">Hahahaha! This book is so out of date, Goodreads doesn't even have a cover image. It's early Tuchman, her break-out book, I believe. As with her other wonderful histories, I learn so much I almost can't believe it. So that's how we got into World War I. So we did save their butts. What would have happened if we didn't? Amazing on so many levels.</span>
